name: Memory Leak!
description:
Oh no!

People's jank code that is assigning variables to the heap is lagging the Tesla Server's compiler, and now people can't even edit it through vim, cause it's so slow!!!

Can you solve the C++ errors that are causing this whole mess, so that we can upload our projects by 11:59 to GitHub and not be late???

Only you can save our grades by playing, MEMORY LEAK!
